aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港同支爆唔爆我就唔撚知<br />\n但你就實聽無人請啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69969ee09f9183eefd9a30fbea36f70db8e7712e","tid":19883,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"物價 樓價會升得更快<br />\n人工就不變(僱主聲稱經濟差)<br />\n本身有樓收租/炒樓果班繼續暴發 普通人就繼續做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5e3abc5cb4b0dc0d67f29f952f2baab76d2bd9","tid":19883,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支五年一定唔爆</blockquote><br />\n如果連你都覺得會爆，咁啲既得利益者點會唔做野?<br />\n所以強國係冇可能爆，最多係經濟疲弱<br />\n除非好似08海嘯咁突然爆啲冇人預到既大鑊野"},{"pid":"41713b2ed856f23b00abe64cc13ca114d94378e9","tid":19883,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd37ebc6ca153d5899bbeb45ae018755a4c93a60","tid":19883,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支五年一定唔爆</blockquote><br />\n如果連你都覺得會爆，咁啲既得利益者點會唔做野?<br />\n所以強國係冇可能爆，最多係經濟疲弱<br />\n除非好似08海嘯咁突然爆啲冇人預到既大鑊野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你已經答左"},{"pid":"3ada2f768234978d645b1b442023183e04cca876","tid":19883,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"經濟同政局有好大關係<br />\n所以大陸死都唔可能俾香港爆<br />\n呢幾年香港經濟一爆個管治權就無<br />\n<br />\n最多就係慢慢陰乾<br />\n食你唔飽餓你唔死"}]}